name: Alive and Kicking
description:
Angga Dwimas Sasongko is a director, a producer; a father; a dreamer and also the one who makes them come true. Some say he was fierce, and others say he was grumpy. But if you look closer, past his rock-solid personality. This man is pure gold.

Long live Angga Dwimas Sasongko.



Sincerely,


Afterlab
